Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透是飯糰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又發生什麼事情了嗎 你是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人又說你什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.46,0:02:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有我 只有我愛著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個百分之百的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我一點也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 其實妳很害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一天內才要確認好幾次看看念珠在不在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最驕傲的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為何不讓我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你長得太可愛了 所以不想讓別人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是覺得丟臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我最愛你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了你 媽媽連死都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實妳根本不認同我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會說一些做母親的冠冕堂皇的話而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽比誰都要愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們…就只能逃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只能逃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠這種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.78,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳快說 快點說出實話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把妳現在想的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點說實話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說洩氣話就說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透妳該照妳的個性去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說些任性的話也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 什麼力量也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很怕這樣的阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後我也想要和你一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起…生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃飯 一起上學 一起煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望你能聽我的任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想聽聽你的洩氣話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想和你一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.25,0:07:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不必…對我付出全部的愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得害怕…也不要緊的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實會害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是看清真正的我的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我母親…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會用愛情這兩個字來敷衍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不想真正看清我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多希望她能和我一起想、一起煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不愛我這醜陋的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以…和我一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.78,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會跟我說這種話的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講出我現在最想聽的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.72,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼像妳這樣的女孩會待在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會為我哭泣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要…謝謝妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連聲招呼都不打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…雖然現在還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但總有一天 "師父你是我的父親"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能挺起胸膛對任何人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…會變成這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是個要人照顧的兒子呢 夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要照妳原本的方法去做就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱騰騰的白飯淋上納豆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就這麼有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 今天吃梭魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我想去看慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.72,0:12:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人剩下的日子不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.93,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他背負著我們整個詛咒的"核"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那是出生時就決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自己也無力改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們能做的事就是順從他的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.64,0:13:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於妳 我不希望妳和他接觸太多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 波鳥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要過去 可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只我啦 還有小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真有膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會生氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底來幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會不知道 只是不敢說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫妳說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是想說希望大家都能一起在那個家和睦地生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.78,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓妳對於介入草摩家一事後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳痛苦 一定要讓妳痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳憔悴消瘦不成人形 然後跪在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也給我搞清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要離開草摩家根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不可以違背我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點說"請您原諒我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說"我再也不會介入草摩家"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您一定很痛苦吧 慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從您生下來那一天就被宣告了死的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是多麼的痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 妳知道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種恐懼是常人無法想像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳、由希和阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定也都很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連波鳥也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人您死了的話 大家會很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會非常難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會難過呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是因為我才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本希望我早點消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了死而誕生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命中注定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰能決定這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明活得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著？這樣子算是活著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定的 注定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒叫妳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不知道你母親死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 快把這女人的記憶消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.81,0:17:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很希望你能一直活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能一直看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 妳別再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不知道什麼是詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠和慊人相遇我真的感到很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家相遇我絕對不會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能多多聆聽慊人你的心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你生氣也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是痛苦或悔恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都很想知道慊人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是活著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.79,0:20:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭老鼠 到底發生什麼事 你快點說清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.56,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我好像太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是關於我肚子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後我一定會告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.45,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後來決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有心理準備啦 可別讓我覺得太無趣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 話還沒說完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在某方面也挺有精神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是 雖然我什麼也幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好今後會找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要找什麼如果能由我們決定就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們無法成功 後面也還有人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是 慢慢來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩菜剩飯也沒關係 快點弄東西給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 妳有在天上看著我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時候我會想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.00,0:21:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會走到比這裡更遠的地方
